    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i checked the logs and there aint nothing there. like, no error codes or anything. that makes it even creepier. if it was just a glitch there would be a log entry for the sensor being offline or something. but the temp just... changes. like it knows. do you think it's possible for these devices to be using some kind of external sensor or maybe something in the wifi signal to pick up on bio-signals or movement? like if they're synced up with each other?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
